      <hedline>
        <hl1>Great Radio Station, Unmentioned</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In covering late-night radio shows (''Night Talkers,'' Jan. 21), how could you completely omit WPKN-FM (89.5) in Bridgeport? It has live, non-commercial, non-''canned'' radio 24 hours a day, seven days a week, with an amazing variety, unlike many other stations, such as the sad example given of WPLR.</p>
        <p>Gabriel Dunn  Newtown</p>
      </block>
